<paragraph base="SL33288" principles="yes" id="IAS39_86"><paranum>86</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 39"/><data name="paranum" value="86"/></prolog><body><p outputclass="keep_with_next" id="IAS39_P0531">Hedging relationships are of three types:</p><ol base="SL134858" type="lower-alpha" id="IAS39_L0048"><li id="IAS39_86_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="SL134860" id="IAS39_P0532"><i>fair value hedge</i>: a hedge of the exposure to           changes in <xref base="SL134652" href="../ifrs13/IFRS13_APPA.dita#IFRS13_APPA/IFRS13_DI0006" scope="local">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> of a recognised           asset or liability or an unrecognised firm commitment, or an identified portion of such an           asset, liability or <xref base="SL134655" href="IAS39_9_hedge-accounting.dita#IAS39_9_hedge-accounting/IAS39_P0208" scope="local">firm commitment<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0131"/></ph></xref>,           that is attributable to a particular risk and could affect profit or loss.</p>                         </li><li id="IAS39_86_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="SL134862" id="IAS39_P0535"><i>cash flow hedge</i>: a hedge of the exposure to           variability in cash flows that (i) is attributable to a particular risk associated with a           recognised asset or liability (such as all or some future interest payments on variable           rate debt) or a highly probable <xref base="SL134656" href="IAS39_9_hedge-accounting.dita#IAS39_9_hedge-accounting/IAS39_P0209" scope="local">forecast transaction<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0138"/></ph></xref> and (ii) could affect profit or loss.</p>                         </li></ol><ol base="F311232" type="lower-alpha" id="IAS39_L0049"><li id="IAS39_86_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="SL134864" id="IAS39_P0539"><i>hedge of a <xref base="SL147532" href="../ias21/IAS21_8.dita#IAS21_8/IAS21_P0037">net investment in a foreign                 operation<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0255"/></ph></xref></i> as defined in <xref base="F389359" href="../ias21/IAS21_TOC.dita" scope="local" id="IAS39_X0490">IAS 21</xref>.</p>                </li></ol></body></paragraph>